  <!-- Purifier Applications -->
  <h3 id="purifier-applications">Purifier Centrifuge Applications</h3>
  <p>In most purifier centrifuge applications, the light phase is the predominant phase, and the heavy phase is a much smaller proportion of the process fluid. The following are some real-world purifier centrifuge applications.</p>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="/lube-oil-centrifuge/">Lube oil separation from water and solids</a></li>
