  <!-- Summary -->
  <h2 id="summary">Summary</h2>
  <p>In summary, a clarifier centrifuge is a simplified version of a purifier centrifuge. The clarifier version is modified to separate the liquid from solids, whereas the purifier centrifuge can separate the primary liquid from another liquid and solids.</p>
